OL,3,CNearly 1,000 speeding offences
OL,4,Crecorded on the A75 last year, new
OL,5,Cdata shows
OL,7,FMore than nine hundred speeding
OL,8,Foffences were recorded on one of the
OL,9,Fregion's busiest roads last year, data
OL,10,Fobtained by ITV News Border shows.
OL,12,FA top speed of 111 mph was recorded on
OL,13,Fthe road last year, almost double the
OL,14,Fnational speed limit for single
OL,15,Fcarriageways.
OL,17,FThere are no average speed cameras on
OL,18,Fthe road. The number of speeding
OL,19,Foffences has increased each year since
OL,20,F2021, according to the data obtained
OL,21,Fvia a Freedom of Information request.
