OL,4,Crecorded on the A75 last year, new
OL,5,Cdata shows
OL,7,FThe rise in speeding offences could be
OL,8,Flinked to an increase in the number of
OL,9,Fdays police vans are in operation on
OL,10,Fthe road - 229 days in 2023, compared
OL,11,Fto 224 in 2021.
OL,13,F"It's a very important road for
OL,14,FScotland and Ireland. It links two
OL,15,Fcountries," said John Miller, a
OL,16,Fhaulage contractor who has worked in
OL,17,Fthe area for over forty years.
OL,19,F"There's a lot to do on the road to
OL,20,Fmake it safe."
