OL,7,FThe A75 stretches 95 miles from Gretna
OL,8,Fto Stranraer, it's used by people
OL,9,Ftravelling across the region, as well
OL,10,Fas freight transport from Scotland to
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland via the port at
OL,12,FCairnryan.
OL,14,FLocal businesses believe if sections
OL,15,Fof the road is closed it can have a
OL,16,Fserious impact on local economy.
