OL,7,FAt wedding venue Laggan, near
OL,8,FGatehouse of Fleet, Managing Director
OL,9,FDuncan McConchie said: "We saw this
OL,10,Fsix weeks ago when there was a tree
OL,11,Fthat the Roads Department believed was
OL,12,Fgoing to fall down and we had to wait
OL,13,Ffor 6 hours for a specialist to come
OL,14,Ffrom Glasgow.
OL,16,F"In the meantime, we had a wedding
OL,17,Fhere. We have a bride with no hair and
OL,18,Fmakeup. Wedding guests can't get here.
OL,19,FOur team can't get here.
