OL,7,F"We were totally stranded and had
OL,8,Fabsolutely no way of anybody accessing
OL,9,Four property. This was where it
OL,10,Fbecomes a lifeline for us, the A75. At
OL,11,Fthe same point, we're so reliant on it
OL,12,Fas a business."
OL,14,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"Targeting speeding is a priority for
OL,16,FPolice Scotland. Officers routinely
OL,17,Fcarry out marked and unmarked patrols
OL,18,Fon the A75, enforcement activity to
OL,19,Fdeter speeding and detect those who
OL,20,Fchoose to break the law."
