OL,7,FIn a statement Transport Scotland
OL,8,Fsaid: "The Scottish and UK Governments
OL,9,Fhad agreed that investment is required
OL,10,Fon the A75.
OL,12,F"The Cabinet Secretary for Transport,
OL,13,FMs Hyslop, has raised the matter with
OL,14,Fthe UK Secretary of State for
OL,15,FTransport confirming our position, and
OL,16,Fwill continue to do so in order to
OL,17,Fsafeguard the ambitions of the South
OL,18,Fof Scotland, and beyond.
